OL,4,CPret a Manger makes staff pay cuts
OL,5,Cpermanent
OL,6, Pret a Manger has told its staff that a
OL,7, temporary pay cut will now be made
OL,8, permanent as trade remains
OL,9, "significantly below" pre-Covid levels.
OL,11,FThe sandwich chain stopped paying
OL,12,Fworkers during their breaks last
OL,13,FSeptember in a effort to cut costs.
OL,15,FHowever, it has now told workers that
OL,16,Fthe measure will be kept in place.
OL,18,FPret said: "This is in no way a
OL,19,Freflection of the hard work of our
OL,20,Fteams and we're incredibly grateful for
OL,21,Ftheir dedication and commitment."
